Ques: A factory manufacturing flywheels for racing cars has 10 machines to make them. The manufacturer knows the correct weight for a flywheel.However, one day one of the machine begons to produce faculty parts either 
underweight or overweight. How can the manufacturer find the faulty machine in only two weightings?

Solu:
The manufacturer must take one flywheel made by each machine, find their total weight and take the weight before and calculate the difference......................
